	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_HOI_AutogunBase">
        <defName>GW_HOI_Gun_LuciferBolter</defName>
        <label>Lucifer Black bolter</label>
        <description>A bolter in service of the elite Lucifer Blacks. Mortal men they are, but their training allows them to handle the heavy weight and recoil of a bolter much better than the average Guardsman. \n\nThe wax and paper marks adorning this weapon are purity seals - written on the paper are prayers and litanies. It symbolises that the object (and, by extension, the person wielding it) is uncorrupted by the degrading influence of Chaos.</description>
        <possessionCount>1</possessionCount>
        <graphicData>
            <drawSize>0.8</drawSize>
            <texPath>LuciferBlack/Weapons/LuciferBlackBolter</texPath>
        </graphicData>
        <soundInteract>Interact_Shotgun</soundInteract>
        <weaponClasses>
            <li>ShortShots</li>
        </weaponClasses>
        <weaponTags>
            <li>ShortShots</li>
            <li>GW_Rippergun</li>
        </weaponTags>
        <statBases>
            <WorkToMake>13000</WorkToMake>
            <Mass>8.4</Mass>
            <AccuracyTouch>0.95</AccuracyTouch>
            <AccuracyShort>0.75</AccuracyShort>
            <AccuracyMedium>0.40</AccuracyMedium>
            <AccuracyLong>0.20</AccuracyLong>
            <RangedWeapon_Cooldown>3.2</RangedWeapon_Cooldown>
        </statBases>
        <costList>
            <Steel>300</Steel>
            <ComponentIndustrial>20</ComponentIndustrial>
            <ComponentSpacer>5</ComponentSpacer>
            <Plasteel>100</Plasteel>
        </costList>
        <recipeMaker>
            <researchPrerequisite>GW_LuciferBlack</researchPrerequisite>
			<recipeUsers Inherit="false">
                <li>HP_AM_MilitarumFabricationBench</li>
            </recipeUsers>
            <skillRequirements>
                <Crafting>14</Crafting>
            </skillRequirements>
            <displayPriority>430</displayPriority>
        </recipeMaker>
        <verbs>
            <li>
                <verbClass>Verb_Shoot</verbClass>
                <hasStandardCommand>true</hasStandardCommand>
                <defaultProjectile>GW_HOI_Bullet_Bolter</defaultProjectile>
                <warmupTime>0.9</warmupTime>
                <range>36</range>
				<burstShotCount>4</burstShotCount>
                <soundCast>GW_Heavy_Bolt_Gun_Sound</soundCast>
                <soundCastTail>GunTail_Medium</soundCastTail>
                <muzzleFlashScale>9</muzzleFlashScale>
            </li>
        </verbs>
        <tools>
            <li>
                <label>stock</label>
                <capacities>
                    <li>Blunt</li>
                </capacities>
                <power>9</power>
                <cooldownTime>2</cooldownTime>
            </li>
            <li>
                <label>barrel</label>
                <capacities>
                    <li>Blunt</li>
                    <li>Poke</li>
                </capacities>
                <power>9</power>
                <cooldownTime>2</cooldownTime>
            </li>
        </tools>
		<!-- <equippedAngleOffset>45</equippedAngleOffset> -->
    </ThingDef>
	
	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_HOI_LasgunBase">
        <defName>GW_HOI_Gun_LuciferHellgun</defName>
        <label>Lucifer Black hellgun</label>
        <description>A hellgun of the Lucifer Blacks, complete with purity seals. An excellent design even before meeting the craftsman’s hands, its powerful lasbolts can stop any who would threaten the Imperial Palace. \n\nPurity seals written by non-Imperial hands are markedly different to those of the Imperium of Man. As well as differences in content - appeals to different gods or even atheistic litanies - the font and materials used are also non-traditional. If such equipment is acquired by Imperial forces and pressed into service, the purity seals are invariably replaced with “proper” ones.</description>
