	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_HOI_LasgunBase">
        <defName>GW_HOI_Gun_LuciferPistol</defName>
        <label>Lucifer Black hellpistol</label>
        <description>A modified hellpistol in the colors of the Lucifer Blacks. Despite its small size, this high-powered laspistol packs a surprising punch. \n\nThe Imperium of Man has some disdain for mimicry of their iconography, such as purity seals. They believe it to be just copying with no understanding of the deeper meaning behind it, an aping of their holy symbols. \n\nIt invariably escapes them that such imitation is the stock-in-trade of the Adeptus Mechanicus, with the meaning of their rituals lost to time and replaced with tech-worship.</description>
